      "rationale": "PIV validation experiments were performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry at all five COU operating points using a blood-analogue fluid. Device geometry and fluid properties match the COU. The validation activities are judged sufficiently relevant to the COU context. Required Level 2 achieved."
