      "rationale": "Pump geometry was digitised from FDA-published CAD files. Fluid properties were measured experimentally (viscosity ±2%, density ±0.5%). One-at-a-time sensitivity analysis on inlet flow rate and rotational speed showed RH varies by < 8% for ±5% perturbations in each input. Required Level 2 achieved."
